{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"32ec7bcc5c","title":"整风随笔","origin":"《四川省右派言论选辑2》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共四川省委宣传部办公室编，1957年7月23日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0e0a63ac66","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0be2c45c1c","name":"钟汝为"},{"id":"a185c9b36c","name":"四川"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4c43728196","type":"title","text":"整风随笔","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"a932c7ce9b","type":"authors","text":"四川钟汝为","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"5f8d18e1ef","type":"subtitle","text":"整风随笔       薇(即省民委干部钟汝为)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"b0f0fd5731","type":"paragraph","text":"整风运动开始，整风壁报出版，编者向我征文；写呢，写不好；不写又不可。没法；想点，写点；随时想起，随时写下；命名随笔。正或错，工或拙，在所不计。若能对整风有一点一滴的帮助，就超出我“聊以塞责”的预料以外。就此开场。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"2e3237a989","type":"subtitle","text":"一、解放前和后","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"5a38856bba","type":"paragraph","text":"亲如手足  回首当年，跟着共产党走，会着党的许多前辈和朋友，如吴玉章、林伯渠、张曙时诸老，和罗世文、陈绍禹、程向予、刘连波……诸同志，见面时，有啥说啥，随问随答，欢悦诚恳，洋溢声音笑貌间。国际国内也好，军事政治也好，工作生活也好，一谈几个钟头，真是天南地北，无所不谈。乃至谈到陈绍禹同志的大礼帽，纹皮鞋，藏青色胖哔叽的礼服。陈答：在延安不是这样打扮，到这里是当外交官哪！大家哄然一笑。回忆前情，真是亲如手足。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"dc30000d45","type":"paragraph","text":"(注：钟在解放前参加过国民党、国民党改组派、复兴社和C．C的“中国文化建设协会”，曾任“清共”委员和“剿匪”第一路政治部宣传科长、政治部付主任等职。)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"27392b9b21","type":"paragraph","text":"相近如冰　解放了，那末多共产党同志来了，真是欢天喜地，敢于在大街上昂头走路了。但，除了50年一、二、三月分经常与李宗林部长接触自由谈话外，因工关系渐渐与更多地党员同志接洽了。结果呢？笑容收敛了，青情严肃了，大家都要作在肚子里选话来说。乃至彼此间相对默然无语。他对我好象有难言之苦，我对他也不知说什么才对。只落得这样的对话。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"3f392f7dd3","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：忙吗？","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"f2bf7e2c10","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：不忙，没……甚么。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"adc90e4083","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：(略作上下左右望)今天天气好啦！","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"c30eda283b","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：(低沉)好！","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"6abedcf38b","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：哈！哈！哈！哈！","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"b9d0897d13","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：(微笑)好！好！","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"a97ffbb8fc","type":"paragraph","text":"这样情绪阻塞，言不由衷，只有勉强的工作关系没有“人”的关系，那能不“相近如冰”呢？","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"8410c28abe","type":"paragraph","text":"这种没有“人味”的生活方式，是消极因素的温床，是积极因素的障碍，双方都值得反省罢。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"8dddb0bf14","type":"subtitle","text":"二、奇异的逻辑","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"01b1acc136","type":"paragraph","text":"几年来，在党群之间，流行了这样一个逻辑：","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"5863a4b4ba","type":"paragraph","text":"“你不满意我，甚至只有一些儿不满意我，你就是反对我。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"1946b927bd","type":"paragraph","text":"我是甚么？","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"b7a5c51f06","type":"paragraph","text":"我是党员，党委，党书，……。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"724a15965b","type":"paragraph","text":"你反对我，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"3d4d1cbf94","type":"paragraph","text":"你就是反对党；","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"e39e19136b","type":"paragraph","text":"反对党就是反人民，反革命！”","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"d29f42375e","type":"paragraph","text":"这个逻辑的第一个前题是：","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"33f9fcbf0c","type":"paragraph","text":"“凡是党员都没有一点缺点和错误的。”","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"17c7f2f520","type":"paragraph","text":"然而党员实不是菩萨。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"e9eb4491cb","type":"paragraph","text":"这个逻辑的第二个前题是：","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"5ae58ea009","type":"paragraph","text":"“我就是党。”","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"fb06f56daf","type":"paragraph","text":"然而党员确实不等于党。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"ea3f3b1f77","type":"paragraph","text":"这个逻辑的收获是：","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"91758d7fa9","type":"paragraph","text":"党员随时可以祭起“反党反人民”的法宝来威吓有意见的群众。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"fcc121db14","type":"paragraph","text":"“我就是党”我当然高人一等。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"df09721c8f","type":"paragraph","text":"我即“高人一等”，我当然在群众之上，不在群众之中。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"41515b73d8","type":"paragraph","text":"“我即在群众之上”我实在值得骄傲，颐指气使，派头十足。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"9871425776","type":"paragraph","text":"群众方面呢？","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"3c1911cca4","type":"paragraph","text":"一部分消沉下去，管他妈的，做一日和尚撞一日钟。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"7ff92af90d","type":"paragraph","text":"一部分不安于消沉，滋长对立情绪。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"b7991f566d","type":"paragraph","text":"一部分奔走逢迎，仰承意旨，吹牛拍马，博得×××的欢心——柔肠媚骨，名利双收。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"69d02a189a","type":"paragraph","text":"同志们：这个逻辑不利于党，不利于党员，不利于群众，头脑清醒、清醒罢。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"3a3289ca09","type":"subtitle","text":"三、仅供参考","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"b14b9c0c4a","type":"paragraph","text":"孟子有这样两句话：","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"4fcd1600bc","type":"paragraph","text":"“君子视臣如手足，则臣视君如腹心；君之视臣如犬马，则臣视君如国人；君之视臣如土芥，则臣视君如寇仇。”","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"70f7306c0d","type":"paragraph","text":"豫让死智伯不死中行氏时，也曾这样申述过他的理由：","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"ad3a26068c","type":"paragraph","text":"“中行氏以众人待我，我故以众人报之；智伯以国士待我，我故以国士报之。”","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"8392d30e6e","type":"paragraph","text":"用现代的话来说：“君”“中行氏”，“智伯”就相当于“领导”。“臣”和“豫让”就相当于“干部”。“视”和“待”就是领导对干部的“看法”和“态度”。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"4311fb262c","type":"paragraph","text":"这就是说：你相信我，我就信赖你。你不信任我，我也不信赖你。你疑我忌我，我同样也疑你忌你，并且防你。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"7b4c5b13ee","type":"paragraph","text":"这样不信，不任；互疑，互忌，思想上的不断摩擦，言语上的不断龃龉，岂但是消极因素的滋长，并且必然的发展为矛盾的对抗。","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"2cb99a1e5a","type":"paragraph","text":"有人说：改善物资待遇可以解决问题。但，也不尽然。须知道人不是完全为吃饭而生活的。四川有句俗话说：","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"b726b1e4b9","type":"paragraph","text":"“人对头”吃水也是甜的。不对头，就是鱼翅海参也味同嚼腊。”","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"320631f86c","type":"paragraph","text":"在白区的地下工作者，十年、二十年，为了工作，受尽艰辛，吃尽苦头，并无一个钱的报酬，为甚么兴高采烈，甘之若饴？可见不是物资报酬问题。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"5f0980ee96","type":"paragraph","text":"问题究竟在那里？请我们敬爱的领导，或管理人事的同志们，从多方面考虑罢。","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"2ef0c56f70","type":"paragraph","text":"知道么？“士为知己者死”谁不愿为社会主义事业流尽最后一滴血。同志！你高高乎在上，绷架子，摆官气，盛气凌人，谁敢接近你？请问：你曾客观地(去掉成见)认识甚么叫“士”？并曾对“士”用了一点点“知”的工夫呢？他们的感觉是“有力无处努”，“有血无处流”，怎能不苦闷，怎能不造成鸿沟呢？","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"f7d717bce4","type":"paragraph","text":"这些话：我得声明，仅供参考。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"c9c508d09b","type":"subtitle","text":"四、“仰体主公意旨”的典型","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"f2c58a33d9","type":"paragraph","text":"北洋军伐头子袁世凯执政的时代，他手下有个红人(现在或叫积极分子——请恕我借用这个名词一下)名叫陈宦，又号二庵。当时是袁世凯的参谋总长。","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"26b74a58e0","type":"paragraph","text":"陈宦为了体帖袁氏的意旨，取得特别信任起见，想了很多巧妙的办法。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"0ed94b0a9c","type":"paragraph","text":"他在平时在同袁世凯闲谈中，就揣摩袁世凯当前要解决些甚么问题。他雇用了几个秘书，把每一问题写成三个或两个不同的方案。放在身上不同的荷包里。","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"345f2c142f","type":"paragraph","text":"当他出席袁世凯主持的国务会议时，静听各方面对这问题的发言，并密切注视着袁世凯的脸色表情，和谈话倾向。他是不正式发言的，他到聚精会神地揣摩袁世凯的意旨合适他身上那个荷包里的方案。","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"b911e13676","type":"paragraph","text":"最后，袁世凯掉头向他问道：","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"c96e1d889b","type":"appellation","text":"“二庵，你有甚么意见？”","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"98967af5f5","type":"paragraph","text":"他就从装着合于袁的意旨的方案的那个荷包里取出来，恭恭敬敬地呈与袁世凯，说道：","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"dc2abdf14f","type":"paragraph","text":"“这里有草得有一个方案，请总统过目。”","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"ea5c3cf9dd","type":"paragraph","text":"袁接来详细看完，微笑、高兴而嘉评的低声说道：","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"f8a0033b05","type":"paragraph","text":"“二庵，真是先获我心！”","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"3aeaf5870c","type":"paragraph","text":"他这样遇事都“先事承旨”，袁世凯把他认为是智囊，宠信逾于段、冯。迨袁世凯布置称皇帝时，把西南重任交给他。他就浩浩荡荡统率曹琨、张敬尧、李长泰等师，冯玉祥、吴佩孚……诸旅，杀进四川来。","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"d72ccf00da","type":"paragraph","text":"时袁军兴，各省皆反，陈宦亦不得不宣布独立。袁世凯接到陈的独立电报，始而拍桌大骂，继而捶胸顿足，终而垂泣而道甲：","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"0d10a564e7","type":"appellation","text":"“二庵负我！二庵负我！！二庵都会负我！！！”","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"15a129b7da","type":"paragraph","text":"老奸巨滑窃国大盗，就是这样被陈宦气死。","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"6d23cd53fa","type":"paragraph","text":"喜欢“顺着说”的朋友们，很可以向陈宦学习，大进一步，“先获我心”。","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"},{"id":"3719450b1a","type":"paragraph","text":"喜欢听“顺耳之言”的朋友们，也请看看袁世凯的下梢头。","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c"}],"page":{"id":"b74c2b90de","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"32ec7bcc5c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}